    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                <pb facs="nei.n1a.10.40-41"/>
                <fw type="curatorial">40</fw>
                <fw type="authorial"></fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Wednesday, April, 28, 1971
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt. -</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>What a great enjoyable evening April 27th was for me.</p> 
                <p>My big regret is that my two grand daughters did not hear and see you give the very wonderful poem "Crazy Horse" in way it could be understood.</p> 
                <p>I have your Lyric and dramatic poems, now. must get Black Elk speaks</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Thank you so much</salute> 
                    <salute>Sincerely</salute>
                    <signed>Blanche A. Cole</signed> 
                    
                    <fw type="address">
                        3102 Fontenelle Blvd
                        Omaha, Nebr. 68104
                    </fw>
                    
                    <note>Hope that K.E.T.V. will have your program "on" in daytime so the
                        children will have chance to see again a big thankyou.</note>
                </closer>
            </div1>
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <ab type="return">
                    Mrs. Argyle I. Cole 
                    3102 Fontenelle Blvd. 
                    Omaha, Nebr. 68104
                </ab> 
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    U.S.POSTAGE SERVICES 
                    PM
                    29 APR
                    1971
                    <unclear/> ZIP CODE WILDLIFE
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="stamp">
                    UNITED STATES 6c
                    4-30-71
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    Dr. John G. Neihardt 
                    K.E.T.V. Douglas St 
                    Omaha, Nebr. 
                    Forward 
                    5835 Vine St
                    Lincoln, Nebr
                    68505
                </ab> 
                
                <note type="authorial">
                    Please forward
                </note> 
                
